{"tid":1089653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高懸64年的33=x3+y3+z3難題找到整數解","createTime":"2019-04-03T02:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T12:18:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f1df7f89078432ade5078209d4e57ba0a95b5bae","tid":1089653,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net/uploads/2019/03/Cube33-2880x1220_HP-2880x1220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FCube33-2880x1220_HP-2880x1220.jpg&h=53c6ce6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ASoz_NuIvP0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FASoz_NuIvP0&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=9e5c9534\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ASoz_NuIvP0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.quantamagazine.org/sum-of-three-cubes-problem-solved-for-stubborn-number-33-20190326/#newsletter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quantamagazine.org%2Fsum-of-three-cubes-problem-solved-for-stubborn-number-33-20190326%2F%23newsletter&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=004c918b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.quantamagazine.org/sum-of-three-cubes-problem-solved-for-stubborn-number-33-20190326/#newsletter</a><br />\n<br />\n1825年，數學家S. Ryley證明任何分數都可以表示為三個分數立方的總和。<br />\n <br />\n1955年，數學家 Louis Mordell假設是否可以對整數或任意數進行相同的操作。換句話說，對於k的每個可能值，是否存在整數k，x，y和z，使得k = x3 + y3 + z3？<br />\n <br />\n求解29 =x3 +y3 +z3 很容易（29 =3^3 +1^3 +1^3 ）。但是解決33 =x3 +y3 +z3 卻讓數論家困惑很長一段時間。自1955年起，他們一直在使用計算機來解決問題。本週布里斯託大學數學家Booker的計算機程式經過三週的運算後解決了這個問題。<br />\n <br />\n解：（8,866,128,975,287,528）^3 -（-8,778,405,442,862,239）^3<br />\n+（-2,736,111,468,807,040）^3 = 33<br />\n <br />\n在Booker找到此解之前，33和42是100以下僅剩的兩個不能表示為三立方體和的整數<br />\n <br />\nk =x3 +y3 +z3是一種丟番圖方程，其未知變數必須取整數。判斷給定的丟番圖方程是否有解的數學方法並不存在，三維立方體問題是丟番圖方程中最簡單的問題之一。<br />\n <br />\n數論家渴望證明k =x3 +y3 +z3 對於每個整數k有無限多個解的猜想(除了被除以9之後餘數為4或5的k)。證明此猜想的工具可能會撬開問題的邏輯，或適用於其他丟番圖方程。像Booker's for 33這樣的結果為這個猜想提供了支持，讓數論家更有信心。"},{"pid":"fd4ddd71d81d8c80eaaac8e9f2001d6e61a76821","tid":1089653,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":43,"score":-43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"實際應用係咩？"},{"pid":"559162f0ff02bc30a99216cb10c05adbf11e9a81","tid":1089653,"uid":136760,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:52:47.000Z","msg":"解嗰度 個減號應該要轉返做加號先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e401f6fc511c8c757c1498a427ced0f846fcc6b8","tid":1089653,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同連登仔講 Diophantine equation"},{"pid":"5943dbc96217967bc684227faa998c97ee897adb","tid":1089653,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />減都得又真係幾難"},{"pid":"cb23a3d84114209a85b7d4b537120238bde8e95d","tid":1089653,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:55:13.000Z","msg":"1999差d睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1804c147452d7e0713489476805a9bc21ee17b8","tid":1089653,"uid":222614,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"用英文啦，中文睇得好辛苦"},{"pid":"e2f7b35f77c5c2dab7e0122a0f3a5a37668eb8d3","tid":1089653,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:18:31.000Z","msg":"無撚聊<br />\n呢啲解到又會有咩改變啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成班數學毒撚係度圍爐"},{"pid":"f400051e3ed77e3036ace832cb7995884a60db27","tid":1089653,"uid":143260,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"e2f7b35f77c5c2dab7e0122a0f3a5a37668eb8d3","tid":1089653,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"citedBy":2,"